We or third-party advertisers may display ads on the services that are customized to your interests based on the activities you engage in online or in the apps on your mobile device. This type of advertisement customization - sometimes described as "interest-based" or "behavioral" online advertisement - is powered by various technologies, including browser cookies, mobile advertising identifiers, and other non-cookie based technologies. Information we gather in compliance with this Privacy Policy can be used for interest-based advertisements and can be shared with our service providers or partners to deliver such customized advertisements. We and our service providers and partners can use cookies and information you enter when registering or otherwise when creating your profile, for example, the kind of investments you are most interested in. To opt out of interest-based advertisements, please visitÂ http://optout.networkadvertising.org/#!/, which allows you to change your browser settings so that you will no longer be served advertisements that are tailored to your preferences.
Text Messages:
By entering your phone number to access the services, you consent to receiving communications from us via SMS and/or MMS messages delivered through an automated telephone dialing system ("Text Service"), whether or not you have subscribed to the national Do Not Call List, a state Do Not Call List, or a company's internal Do Not Call List. You may need to respond to an initial message to finish your sign-up and validate your enrollment in the text service. By giving us your cell phone or other telephone number, you consent to Social Social Apps and its affiliates to contact you at any phone number you have given us with automatic or pre-recorded calls and text messages in order to: (i) notify you concerning your account; (ii) resolve problems with your account; (iii) settle a dispute; (iv) collect a debt; (v) request your opinion through surveys or questionnaires; (vi) provide you with any updates, alerts, messages, and information for which you have subscribed; and (vii) as otherwise required to service your account or enforce the Terms and Conditions, our policies, applicable law, or any other agreements we have with you. We may also contact you with automated or pre-recorded calls and text messages for marketing related matters (e.g., offers and promotions) if you agree to such communication. In case you decide to change or inactivate your mobile phone number, you commit to promptly update your Social Social Apps account information to assure that your messages are not sent to the person that takes over your old number.
